==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Industrialism
<hw>In*dus"tri*al*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Devotion to industrial pursuits; labor; industry.</def> <rj><au>J.
S. Mill.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The principles or policy applicable to industrial
pursuits or organized labor.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Industrialism</qex> must not confounded with
industriousness.</q> <rj><qau>H. Spencer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>industrialize</ent>⟦br⟧
